only out of concern for...

1146
01:33:55,289 --> 01:33:56,756
...Kaveriamma's well being.

1147
01:33:56,957 --> 01:33:58,584
If you were so concerned

1148
01:33:58,959 --> 01:34:01,427
then where were you when she
was in an Old Age Home?

1149
01:34:01,629 --> 01:34:03,893
It was I who traced her
and got her here.

1150
01:34:04,298 --> 01:34:06,926
Maybe, that's because

1151
01:34:07,201 --> 01:34:10,295
you needed someone to take
care of Chikku and your house.

1152
01:34:14,974 --> 01:34:16,601
Why did you come back?

1153
01:34:18,144 --> 01:34:19,941
Why did you have to come back?

1154
01:34:22,148 --> 01:34:24,116
We were so happy.

1155
01:34:25,652 --> 01:34:27,813
You have everything in life.

1156
01:34:30,156 --> 01:34:34,115
